            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01AZZU1NEnmr3vktUCMhsKPt\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! I've successfully optimized the index.html file with proper SEO meta tags. Here's what I updated:\\n\\n## Changes Made:\\n\\n### 1. **Title Tag** (49 characters - under 60 ✓)\\n- **New**: \\\"Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams\\\"\\n- More concise and keyword-focused while staying under the 60-character limit\\n\\n### 2. **Meta Description** (159 characters - within 150-160 range ✓)\\n- Compelling copy that includes:\\n  - Core benefit: \\\"Automatically find meeting times across time zones\\\"\\n  - Pain point solution: \\\"End the back-and-forth\\\"\\n  - Social proof: \\\"Join 2,000+ teams who cut scheduling time by 80%\\\"\\n  - Clear value prop: \\\"Connect calendar, share availability, done\\\"\\n\\n### 3. **Favicon**\\n- Updated to use the logo image (PNG format) with absolute URL\\n- Changed from `/favicon.ico` to the provided logo URL\\n\\n### 4. **Open Graph Tags** (Facebook, LinkedIn)\\n- ✓ og:title - Matches the main title\\n- ✓ og:description - Matches meta description\\n- ✓ og:image - Uses logo with absolute URL\\n- ✓ og:url - Canonical URL (placeholder for user's domain)\\n- ✓ og:type - Set to \\\"website\\\"\\n\\n### 5. **Twitter Card Tags**\\n- ✓ twitter:card - Set to \\\"summary_large_image\\\"\\n- ✓ twitter:title - Matches main title\\n- ✓ twitter:description - Matches meta description\\n- ✓ twitter:image - Uses logo with absolute URL\\n\\n### 6. **Canonical Link**\\n- ✓ Present and properly formatted (user will need to update with actual domain)\\n\\nAll meta tags are now optimized for search engines and social media sharing, with compelling copy based on the brainstorm context targeting remote teams and distributed companies.\\n\\n**SEO_OPTIMIZED**\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1201,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":10504,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":1201,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":468,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
