            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01PRuaGwt7WUssQ3eYw2x1X5\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! I've successfully optimized the index.html file with comprehensive SEO meta tags. Here's what I added:\\n\\n## SEO Optimizations Applied:\\n\\n### ✅ Basic SEO\\n- **Title**: \\\"Smart Meeting Scheduler for Distributed Teams | TimeSync\\\" (59 characters - under 60 limit)\\n- **Meta Description**: 155 characters highlighting the key value proposition and social proof\\n- **Canonical URL**: Added for proper indexing\\n\\n### ✅ Open Graph Tags (Facebook, LinkedIn)\\n- og:type, og:url, og:title, og:description\\n- og:image using the second image (better for social sharing)\\n\\n### ✅ Twitter Card Tags\\n- twitter:card set to \\\"summary_large_image\\\"\\n- All required Twitter meta tags with consistent messaging\\n\\n### ✅ Favicon\\n- Updated to use the logo image (first image) with proper absolute URL\\n\\n### 🎯 SEO Copy Strategy\\nThe meta tags emphasize:\\n- **Pain point**: \\\"Eliminate scheduling chaos across time zones\\\"\\n- **Target audience**: \\\"Distributed Teams\\\" and \\\"Remote teams\\\"\\n- **Social proof**: \\\"2,000+ companies\\\" and \\\"15+ hours weekly\\\"\\n- **Clear value**: Automatic meeting time optimization\\n\\nAll image URLs use absolute HTTPS URLs as required, and the copy is optimized for both search engines and social media engagement.\\n\\n**SEO_OPTIMIZED**\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":6,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":979,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":10028,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":979,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":324,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
