            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01Cfjgqgb37NPMJ84VhHGsan\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Perfect! All components are properly instrumented. Let me create a final summary:\\n\\n## FIXED\\n\\nI've successfully added L10.createLead() instrumentation to the landing page. Here's what was implemented:\\n\\n### Components Updated:\\n\\n1. **Hero.tsx** ✅\\n   - Added `L10.createLead(email)` for the main hero signup form\\n   - Implemented form submission handler with loading, success, and error states\\n   - Shows success message after lead capture\\n   - Handles errors gracefully with user-friendly messages\\n\\n2. **CTA.tsx** ✅\\n   - Added `L10.createLead(email)` for the call-to-action section\\n   - Implemented form submission handler with loading, success, and error states\\n   - Shows success message after lead capture\\n   - Handles errors gracefully\\n\\n3. **Pricing.tsx** ✅\\n   - Added `L10.createLead(email, { value: tierPrice })` with tier pricing for ROAS tracking\\n   - Implemented modal-based email capture when users click pricing tier buttons\\n   - Passes tier price values: Free ($0), Founder ($49), Studio ($299)\\n   - Studio plan redirects to sales email (contact sales flow)\\n   - Shows success message after lead capture\\n\\n### Key Features Implemented:\\n\\n✅ **Proper L10 Integration**: All email capture points use `L10.createLead()`\\n✅ **ROAS Tracking**: Pricing tiers pass `{ value: tierPrice }` for accurate conversion value tracking\\n✅ **Error Handling**: All forms handle errors gracefully and show user-friendly messages\\n✅ **Loading States**: Buttons show \\\"Submitting...\\\" during API calls\\n✅ **Success States**: Clear success messages shown after lead capture\\n✅ **Form Validation**: Email fields are required and properly validated\\n✅ **Google Ads Conversion**: L10 library automatically fires Google Ads conversion tracking on success\\n\\nThe landing page is now fully instrumented and ready to track leads and conversions!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":201,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":27405,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":201,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":469,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
